      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to address common floor pan fatigue, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While showing minor aesthetic wear, the powertrain remains robust, with a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response that defines the analog driving experience.",
